### 대기열 진입 — 응답 token이 이후 요청에 자동 저장됨
POST http://localhost:8080/api/queue/join

> {%
    client.global.set("token", response.body.token);
%}

### 내 상태 조회 (WAITING / ELIGIBLE / ACTIVE / EXPIRED / NOT_FOUND)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/queue/me?token=2413d462-2d8b-454c-9193-c29814e70848

### 입장 확정 (ELIGIBLE 상태에서만 CLAIMED)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/queue/claim
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{token}}"
}

### 예매 (ACTIVE 상태에서만 COMPLETED)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{token}}"
}

### 대기열 전체 상태 관찰 (admin)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/queue

### 검증 오류 확인 — 토큰 누락 400
POST http://localhost:8080/api/queue/claim
Content-Type: application/json

{}
